-- Xstrata Starts Construction of $151 Million Bracemac-Mcleod Mine in Canada
-- Amanda Jordan
-- 2010-07-09T16:13:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/xstrata-starts-construction-of-151-million-bracemac-mcleod-mine-in-canada.html

          
          
             Xstrata Zinc Canada started building
the $151 million Bracemac-McLeod mine, which at full production
will yield 80,000 metric tons of zinc and 10,000 tons of copper
a year.  
 Output will begin in early 2012 and full production is
expected in the first quarter of 2013. Â   
